{"tid":2178804,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)冬蔭功 拳霸 女拳霸","createTime":"2020-08-28T15:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T20:36:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1a4b4e4bd96fccd932e32cd334f81a09964ef8","tid":2178804,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=e43ced26\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=7203a0bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=1f38bb22\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://bestmartialartsmovies.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/tony-jaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbestmartialartsmovies.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2Ftony-jaa.jpg&h=95515d61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a7/HKFilm_JiJaYanin1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa7%2FHKFilm_JiJaYanin1.jpg&h=b40ec73d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事講述在一個泰國寧靜的村落裏，純樸善良的阿錦（東尼嘉）與父親相依為命，他們過著簡單而開心的生活。當年曾擔任泰王御兵的父親閒時還會教授御兵所操練的拳術予阿錦，希望他日練成後可以為國王效力。<br />\n此外，兩父子並計劃將家中飼養的大象呈獻給國王。在潑水節前夕，父親雀躍地跟村長商量如何將心愛的象呈獻給國皇，豈料村長另有圖謀，與壞人互相勾結，藉口把大象送往身體檢查，把大象運往澳洲作黑市交易..<br />\n<br />\n2.朗．柏都（Nong Pra-Du）為泰國一寧靜小村莊，村民信奉佛教，尤其是寺內的安北佛（Ong Bak）。可惜，無良村民阿堂砍掉安北佛的頭，賣予不法商人謀取暴利，全村頓時恐懼不安。看守佛寺的阿丁，決定單人匹馬前赴曼谷，誓要將佛頭奪回&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.自閉症少女雪（Sen，琴嘉飾）自小與母親珊本（Sin）相依為命。珊本為泰國黑幫頭目八哥的手下，因與日本黑幫頭目岸本（Masashi，阿部寬飾）相戀，兩人被泰國黑道中人視為眼中釘，誓要除之而後快。岸本為保性命，不得已玩美女人日本。珊本母女四處逃避，卻依然難逃黑幫魔掌.....<br />\n<br />\n11 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=01eda02a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=b7d4da97\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35d7317ee0829bb85d11a071be00d8dfb865196","tid":2178804,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal